column5: 16 M, haven’t talk to someone here in a while and feeling like I should
I do feel like I truely have depression but I don’t really tell anyone bc I think to know exactly you do have to go somewhere to check it out.
Hope u ok and that you won’t do it again.

Damn man. Hopefully you get the help and specially the support you need. I’m really sorry about your parents, it gotta be really hard being there. I’m in a really bad situation as well but I think there might be something good waiting for us. Maybe someday you get the chance to get the happiness you want without heading out. Good luck bro.
Maybe a couple people but I don’t feel any better.
I can’t, my parents won’t let me drive and that think it’s not big of a deal. Not annoying tho.
Glad you good bro. Keep it up.
I've had enough experiences knowing how is it going to be like you know, but i feel like it would destroy my friends and family so I'm still here
